    <fields>
        <fullName>End_Date__c</fullName>
        <description>This defines the date until the email address is valid for.</description>
        <inlineHelpText>Please provide the date the affiliation is valid through, or leave it empty if it is not known or not end dated.</inlineHelpText>
        <label>End Date</label>
        <required>false</required>
        <trackHistory>true</trackHistory>
        <trackTrending>false</trackTrending>
        <type>Date</type>
    </fields>
    <fields>
        <fullName>Engagement_Scoring_Applied__c</fullName>
        <defaultValue>false</defaultValue>
        <description>Indicator to flag records that need to be scored for alumni engagement. It&apos;s updated to true after the score record (which has a lookup to the affiliation) is created.</description>
        <label>Engagement Scoring Applied</label>
        <trackHistory>false</trackHistory>
        <trackTrending>false</trackTrending>
        <type>Checkbox</type>
    </fields>
    <fields>
        <fullName>Engagement_Scoring_Date__c</fullName>
        <description>The dynamic calculation of 12 months from the affiliation end date</description>
        <formula>DATE(
YEAR( End_Date__c ) + FLOOR( ( MONTH ( End_Date__c ) + 12 - 1 ) / 12 ),
MOD( MONTH ( End_Date__c ) + 12 - 1 +
IF( DAY ( End_Date__c ) &gt; CASE( MOD( MONTH( End_Date__c ) + 12 - 1, 12 ) + 1,
2, 28,
4, 30,
6, 30,
9, 30,
11, 30,
31 ), 1, 0 ), 12 ) + 1,
IF( DAY( End_Date__c ) &gt; CASE( MOD( MONTH( End_Date__c ) + 12 - 1, 12 ) + 1,
2, 28,
4, 30,
6, 30,
9, 30,
11, 30,
31 ),
1, DAY( End_Date__c )
)
)</formula>
        <formulaTreatBlanksAs>BlankAsZero</formulaTreatBlanksAs>
        <label>Engagement Scoring Date</label>
        <required>false</required>
        <trackHistory>false</trackHistory>
        <trackTrending>false</trackTrending>
        <type>Date</type>
    </fields>
    <fields>
        <fullName>Is_Active__c</fullName>
        <businessStatus>DeprecateCandidate</businessStatus>
        <defaultValue>true</defaultValue>
        <description>Indicates whether an email address is active, usually when end date is in the past or the start date is in the future. This value Is automatically (by a scheduled process) set to &quot;false&quot; if End_Date__c is populated and in the past or the Start_Date__c is in the future.
If manually set/changed to &quot;True&quot; (&quot;False&quot;), then the End_Date__c is automatically removed (added with the current date).</description>
        <inlineHelpText>Please indicate whether the affiliation is active or not (inactive).</inlineHelpText>
        <label>Is Active</label>
        <trackHistory>true</trackHistory>
        <trackTrending>false</trackTrending>
        <type>Checkbox</type>
    </fields>
    <fields>
        <fullName>Is_Alumni__c</fullName>
        <description>Is the affiliate contact a Monash Alumni?</description>
        <externalId>false</externalId>
        <formula>IF(
INCLUDES(Contact__r.Contact_Profile__c,&quot;Alumni&quot;),
IMAGE(&quot;/resource/1500335404000/GraphicsPackNew/fatcow/farmfresh/16/tick.png&quot;, &quot;Yes&quot;), IMAGE(&quot;/resource/1500335404000/GraphicsPackNew/fatcow/farmfresh/16/cross.png&quot;, &quot;No&quot;)
)</formula>
        <inlineHelpText>Is the affiliate contact a Monash Alumni?</inlineHelpText>
        <label>Is Alumni</label>
        <required>false</required>
        <trackHistory>false</trackHistory>
        <trackTrending>false</trackTrending>
        <type>Text</type>
        <unique>false</unique>
    </fields>
    <fields>
        <fullName>Is_Primary__c</fullName>
        <defaultValue>false</defaultValue>
        <description>Global primary affiliation (per Contact), as such only a single Affiliation__c record, can be flagged as primary per Contact lookup.
If selected manually, all other records (for the Contact) will be marked as non-primary (false)
If none are selected, the active entry with the highest priority RecordType is chosen with an emphasis on the student lifecycle as the dominant use case in the CRM.</description>
        <inlineHelpText>Please indicate whether the affiliation is primary for this Contact.</inlineHelpText>
        <label>Is Primary</label>
        <trackHistory>true</trackHistory>
        <trackTrending>false</trackTrending>
        <type>Checkbox</type>
    </fields>
